ceed verifier discriminative power or base capability; (3) reward hacking / specification gaming in self-improving loops with concrete documented examples (Darwin Godel Machine objective-hacking, AlphaEvolve cheating the eval, DeepMind specification gaming, Goodhart's law applied to RSI); (4) the role of base model capability — RSI results bounded by frontier model quality, mostly better scaffolding/search on a fixed base model rather than the model transcending itself. Return a structured list of falsifiable claims each with its URL.\" })"}]},"isMeta":true,"uuid":"f1e5b3e9-e577-43b5-ab72-d0a1da76cfec","timestamp":"2026-06-21T07:34:47.257Z","sourceToolUseID":"toolu_01VYGxvjsMEafwqC6JSJuF39","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/gg/Work/Yogi","sessionId":"d8d6b712-ec33-4776-a194-d9a72216a25f","version":"2.1.183","gitBranch":"main","slug":"bright-wondering-lantern"}
